es over them. Furthermore, we construct the Grassmannian\nconnection on the projective modules $\\Xi^\\prime$ with trace $2\\nu$ over the\nQHMs and compute its corresponding curvature, and we construct a tensor product\nconnections on $P E^c_{\\mu\\nu}\\otimes \\Xi$ whose coupling constant is $2\\nu$\nand characterize the critical points of YM for this projective module.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Oct 2018 13:21:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Mar 2019 01:37:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-26"}
